quarks.connectors.iot

Interface QoS


  • public interface QoS
    Device event quality of service levels. The QoS levels match the MQTT specification.
    An implementation of IotDevice may not support all QoS levels.
    See Also:
    mqtt.org, IotDevice.events(quarks.topology.TStream, String, int), IotDevice.events(quarks.topology.TStream, quarks.function.Function, quarks.function.UnaryOperator, quarks.function.Function)
